itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"好細字，有冇放大版？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"我影左一張就急急腳走咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以㩒入去放大睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"大概意思寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"大概就係話話太古鐵站入面發射tg之後，太古地鐵站做呢啲善後工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐講廢話 敷衍下你地咁囉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKkd8LL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKkd8LL.png&h=307f553f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3751fa130e585328e0bb92bd66b4873805c32b65","tid":1480081,"uid":12130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=34896841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=34896841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"b6a30d4d4095c4e4d36a4bb322e649a9a76b0cf2","tid":1480081,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74ad1ea98df7f79370d8cc84ef481f6065515b9","tid":1480081,"uid":226064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"369fedbe97a4330f87a586d8917c46a6d39f76a4","tid":1480081,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea66141c3d3defb5f385e573aae71c13808c47fc","tid":1480081,"uid":226064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"我影左一張就急急腳走咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以㩒入去放大睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"大概意思寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"大概就係話話太古鐵站入面發射tg之後，太古地鐵站做呢啲善後工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐講廢話 敷衍下你地咁囉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKkd8LL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKkd8LL.png&h=307f553f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"冇得評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 